<h2 id="options-and-switches">Options and Switches</h2>
<p>When calling <code>choco list -lo</code>:</p>
<pre><code class="language-none">   --audit, --showaudit, --show-audit, --show-audit-info
   Show Audit Information - Display auditing information for a package.
